WEBVTT

00:00:00.151 --> 00:00:03.417
To ground this, engage in a rigorous analytical challenge.

00:00:04.058 --> 00:00:07.082
Identify a recent leadership failure within your organization.

00:00:07.784 --> 00:00:11.369
Map the root cause of that failure to a specific value in congruence.

00:00:12.231 --> 00:00:13.954
What objective variables were present?

00:00:14.535 --> 00:00:16.257
What was the root cause hypothesis?

00:00:16.898 --> 00:00:18.802
What solution variables were analyzed?

00:00:19.703 --> 00:00:25.733
Deploying structured cognitive protocols under pressure ensures analytical precision over reactive assumptions.
